98","tid":1518521,"uid":304321,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"你班狗都痴撚線架 小妹我就住港島既 依家星期六想去行個街拍下拖見下朋友又話犯法 一陣又鎖撚埋黨鐵咁我點呀?<br />\n你不如宣佈聽日港島區宵禁啦你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"住港島既出個門口都非法集結"},{"pid":"fdf3acaec3670416a2815a129e71a9314b48257c","tid":1518521,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"實有人唔參與運動 去銅鑼灣番工架喎"},{"pid":"36c6530ae310e424d3fc0497f7e26a861c66e82b","tid":1518521,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:11:26.000Z","msg":"行街都犯法？"},{"pid":"1d7577ef2ea2375f271a6d2837132e7ca1fc96a5","tid":1518521,"uid":294783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"你咁樣講，人地明明冇諗住去行街都即刻改變主意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分分鐘train到D&quot;和理非&quot;都突然進化變身成&quot;游擊和理非&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一陣九龍淪陷都唔知點算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5206a7bae2c1bc1e24c289c7a9ffd020ef9043b","tid":1518521,"uid":292424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"違你老母 告我行街啊 <br />\n條街多人得濟逼出馬路又拉啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043f7fc3aed482874a8a22d5cc04bdbbb0850db2","tid":1518521,"uid":13318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"ea9fe0805e810e655b27222c697818a3996e013e","tid":1518521,"uid":169169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:16:11.000Z","msg":"唔行出行人路就絕對無事"},{"pid":"62dfa6a0295c897e2db5aa5d63ffa006fe828c22","tid":1518521,"uid":82530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:17:26.000Z","msg":"你咁樣做係唔會令到我驚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccda0744b7f89365081ddf264d89e9d77888bdd8","tid":1518521,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:19:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a1de4a699848ee0ccd5af5fe35df97dcd74175","tid":1518521,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b67b6ccb6071a217d0257729e969780217539e","tid":1518521,"uid":299920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:26:22.000Z","msg":"和理非都可以 be water<br />\nbe water 式遊行<br />\n<br />\n不需摳泥邊一個站 (港島優先)，出站後沿行車方向在行人路（人太多可能要落一落馬路），行落下一個地鐵站再入站，再係另一個地鐵站出閘再行過。<br />\n<br />\n詳細少少：　以黑衫或者標語為認，或者簡單Ｄ，離開車廂時以手掩單眼為認。出站後沿行車方向在行人路行，我係哩邊路由金鐘行去中環，你可以係對面行車線由中環行去金鐘，沿路你可以舉標語叫口號，或者以手掩單眼。咁樣會行得流暢Ｄ，同整齊到唔係各自行街。<br />\n<br />\n行一個站後就入返地鐵坐去另一個站再行過。佢封邊個站就ｓｋｉｐ左佢去另一個站，我就唔信你封晒全九龍＋港島地鐵站。<br />\n由晏晝三點行到夜晚九點倒　和理非遊行可以收工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁樣有意識地各自行一個站好十幾轉，我睇下你點話我非法集結！"},{"pid":"3d1eeba758c7d376e5c8b84f0b8d091d0fe4e319","tid":1518521,"uid":202095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5rCnEX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5rCnEX.gif&h=5b025a4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97b19271757cb9fb9846745be4debd5e9dcf165f","tid":1518521,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"我就出黎搏拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警你記得拉尻我我一定屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e77c971ccc8764ad77aabed5f36582a26102f74","tid":1518521,"uid":271420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor